Package: TranscriptoPathR
Title: A Comprehensive Shiny App for RNA-Seq Analysis
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alpay", "Temiz", email = "temizna@umn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    TranscriptoPathR provides an interactive Shiny interface for complete RNA-Seq analysis,
    including data upload, normalization, quality control, differential expression,
    gene expression visualization, pathway analysis, simple clustering with PCA, Cancer Gene Census overlaps,
    transcription factor enrichment and GSEA, GSVA and ssGSVA using CRAN and Bioconductor tools.
